{"tid":2302955,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【社區資訊】推動九龍城區議會試行社區參與式預算","createTime":"2020-11-27T13:46:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-27T13:50:02.000Z","uid":138409,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0879db570bffb90848c5e7cbfb290e4b709758ac","tid":2302955,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T13:46:11.000Z","msg":"阿葆<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Whampaper/videos/171122251208212\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FWhampaper%2Fvideos%2F171122251208212&d=jO1S1Ej7eDj8oQYGBWUFpN3lGhCGuGi3hvupoSMmYHA%3D&h=a972b651\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/Whampaper/videos/171122251208212</a><br />\n<br />\n過往九龍城區議會的撥款及預算，大部分皆由區議員、九龍城民政事務處及其他相關政府部分來決定，居民的參與度低，亦未必瞭解區議會的撥款運用在甚麼項目。<br />\n為處理區議會撥款與地區民情脫鉤的情況，葆議員及關醫師均希望能於九龍城區議會中推動試行社區參與式預算，透過公開討論，讓居民就區內活動、工作小組、社區發展及物資派發等預算安排提出意見，然後決定部分預算撥款的用途，以凝聚社區力量，並促進區議會於功能上更能貼合社區需要。<br />\n作為試行社區參與式預算的第一步，我們設立了九龍城區議會撥款修改器的網頁，讓居民認識更多有關九龍城區議會撥款最新財政狀況，居民亦可以提交他們心目中理想的撥款預算，係準備來年預算是作參考，希望透過集體智慧，讓撥款能真正惠及居民。<br />\n九龍城區議會撥款修改器網址： <a href=\"https://kwongpoyin.github.io/kowlooncity-budget-plan/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkwongpoyin.github.io%2Fkowlooncity-budget-plan%2F&d=jO1S1Ej7eDj8oQYGBWUFpN3lGhCGuGi3hvupoSMmYHA%3D&h=c0f30b40\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://kwongpoyin.github.io/kowlooncity-budget-plan/</a><br />\n特別鳴謝：Ho Wa Wong 黃浩華 技術支援"},{"pid":"0749f7b675faedfb5a8ec835f1fc4af03d475ef3","tid":2302955,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T13:46:24.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"82ac5a0f1758e487dea8d58ae81ffa0d8bae9a75","tid":2302955,"uid":311128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T13:46:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"550f6f1